      • getDomainFavicons

        public java.util.Set<java.net.URL> getDomainFavicons()
        Returns a list of URLs created by appending common favicon filenames to the root of the page URL. E.g. http://example.com/index.html will give http://example.com/favicon.ext where ext is one of:
        • ico
        • png
        • gif
